                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-91-off530 t18080601-91-cd531"></join>, a leather trunk, value 10 s. three waistcoats, value 8 s. two pair of breeches, value 12 s. a pair of drawers, value 1 s. and a yard and a half of brown holland, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18080601-91-victim766" type="victimName">
